        <!--ㅜㅜㅜㅜㅜㅜㅜㅜㅜㅜㅜㅜㅜㅜㅜㅜㅜ스타일ㅜㅜㅜㅜㅜㅜㅜㅜㅜㅜㅜㅜㅜㅜㅜㅜㅜㅜㅜㅜ-->
        <!--그림자 이펙트-->
        <DropShadowEffect x:Key="shadowEffect" Direction="135" ShadowDepth="1" Opacity="0.2"  BlurRadius="20"/>
        <!--토글 감추는 스타일(현재 안쓰임)-->
        <Style x:Key="ExpandCollapseToggleStyle" TargetType="{x:Type ToggleButton}">
            <Setter Property="Visibility" Value="Collapsed"/>
        </Style>
        <!--대화 트리아이템 스타일-->
        <Style TargetType="{x:Type TreeViewItem}" x:Key="styleTreeViewContainerDaehwa">
            <Setter Property="IsExpanded" Value="True"/>
            <Setter Property="Background" Value="{Binding Source={StaticResource myOption}, Path=DataInstence.skin.mentionOne, Mode=OneWay}"/>
            <!--<Style.Triggers>
                <Trigger Property="ItemsControl.AlternationIndex" Value="0">
                    <Setter Property="Background" 
                        Value="{Binding Source={StaticResource myOption}, Path=DataInstence.skin.mentionOne, Mode=OneWay}">
                    </Setter>
                </Trigger>
                <Trigger Property="ItemsControl.AlternationIndex" Value="1">
                    <Setter Property="Background" 
                        Value="{Binding Source={StaticResource myOption}, Path=DataInstence.skin.mentionTwo, Mode=OneWay}">
                    </Setter>
                </Trigger>
                <Trigger Property="IsMouseOver" Value="True">
                    --><!--마우스오버 시 색상--><!--
                    <Setter Property="Background" Value="{DynamicResource {x:Static SystemColors.HighlightBrushKey}}" />
                </Trigger>
            </Style.Triggers>-->
        </Style>

        <!--트리뷰 아이템 스타일-->
        <Style TargetType="{x:Type TreeViewItem}" x:Key="styleTreeViewContainer">
            <Setter Property="IsExpanded" Value="True"/>
            <Setter Property="Margin" Value="-20,0,0,0"/>
            <Setter Property="ItemsPanel">
                <Setter.Value>
                    <ItemsPanelTemplate>
                        <template:MyVirtualizingStackPanel x:Name="virtual"/>
                    </ItemsPanelTemplate>
                </Setter.Value>
            </Setter>
            <Style.Triggers>
                <Trigger Property="ItemsControl.AlternationIndex" Value="0">
                    <Setter Property="Background" 
                        Value="{Binding Source={StaticResource myOption}, Path=DataInstence.skin.blockOne, Mode=OneWay}">
                    </Setter>
                </Trigger>
                <Trigger Property="ItemsControl.AlternationIndex" Value="1">
                    <Setter Property="Background" 
                        Value="{Binding Source={StaticResource myOption}, Path=DataInstence.skin.blockTwo, Mode=OneWay}">
                    </Setter>
                </Trigger>
                <Trigger Property="IsMouseOver" Value="True">
                    <!--마우스오버 시 색상-->
                    <Setter Property="Background" Value="{DynamicResource {x:Static SystemColors.HighlightBrushKey}}" />
                </Trigger>
            </Style.Triggers>
        </Style>

